//Instruction page// Instructions: Welcome to Battleship! Press the Start Game button on the menu page to begin a game. Follow the prompts to place your ship and attack the opponent. There is a two length Destroyer, a three length Submarine, a three length Cruiser, and a four length Battleship. Make sure not to overlap your ships!If they fall off the board, they will wrap around. Upon attack, the square chosen will turn to a \' if the attack was unsuccessful, and a x if an enemy ship has been hit. Sink all the enemy ships before they sink yours to win! Press the back button to go back to the menu and start a game. Back to Menu
